Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.93,0:01:51.20,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fad(100,200)}翻譯 十六夜剎那 後期 秋月 暮葉 OPED歌詞協力 灰羽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.94,0:00:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.56,0:00:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是卡辛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.12,0:00:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露娜 殺了妳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//-------------------OP-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.98,0:01:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那天開始的 毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.39,0:01:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從殺死露娜的那一瞬間開始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.40,0:01:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的世界開始了無可奈何般的毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.92,0:01:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺人者 名為卡辛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.92,0:01:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 是卡辛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.21,0:01:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他必須要收拾這個世界的殘局
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.37,0:01:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}（殺死卡辛）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.25,0:02:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一話 在終結的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.89,0:02:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給這個世界帶來毀滅的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.04,0:02:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡辛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.17,0:03:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃掉卡辛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.68,0:03:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺死…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.92,0:03:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺死卡辛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.21,0:03:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃掉卡辛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.79,0:03:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何 吃了我又怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.92,0:03:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毀滅停止不下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.55,0:03:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的身體 卡辛即使不被你幹掉也會在半年内毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.36,0:03:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這和我有什麽關係
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.27,0:04:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡辛 吃了你會得到永恒的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:04:01.00,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}嗯 唐僧肉？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.80,0:04:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.39,0:04:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不清楚真假
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.33,0:04:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不掙扎就這麽去死那太悲慘了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.52,0:04:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.14,0:04:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毀滅停不下來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.19,0:04:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了我會得到永恒的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.27,0:05:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺死卡辛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.06,0:05:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃掉卡辛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.83,0:05:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺死卡辛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.55,0:05:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃掉卡辛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.52,0:05:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺死卡辛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.79,0:05:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了意志就會這麽脆弱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.55,0:05:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確 是個脆弱的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.88,0:05:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有機械人的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.16,0:06:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歐吉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.50,0:06:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林檎 醒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.72,0:06:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不多睡點可不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.90,0:06:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.27,0:06:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃掉卡辛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.01,0:06:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的傳言
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.49,0:06:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了又怎麽樣 毀滅又停止不下來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.38,0:07:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.22,0:07:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毀滅已經開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.66,0:07:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得不收拾的殘局也已經開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.64,0:07:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡辛 還有我們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺醒了嗎 卡辛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.94,0:07:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的 你暫時也會生意興隆了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.42,0:08:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.43,0:08:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.37,0:08:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.57,0:08:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥是人類嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.28,0:09:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 就是機械人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.61,0:09:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.54,0:09:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.18,0:09:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.43,0:09:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 我沒怎麽見過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.55,0:09:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 覺得哥哥也許就是 因為好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.67,0:09:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 叫什麽名字
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.15,0:09:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.42,0:09:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫林檎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.42,0:09:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是林檎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.49,0:09:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.06,0:09:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺死卡辛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.04,0:10:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺死卡辛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.32,0:10:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡辛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.20,0:10:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡辛？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.62,0:10:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海浪欺負人！好不容易排好的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.54,0:11:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳也是機械人？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.16,0:11:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 這裡生銹了歐吉幫我修好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.93,0:11:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來會更漂亮 現在不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.06,0:11:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為毀滅開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.31,0:11:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毀滅是什麽 林檎也會毀滅嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.37,0:11:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不通 不過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.41,0:12:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥真的好漂亮 不像我那麽破爛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.18,0:12:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像人類
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.51,0:12:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.24,0:12:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歐吉會擔心的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.32,0:12:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歐吉會擔心的 歐吉會擔心的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.54,0:12:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.61,0:12:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.51,0:12:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不覺得妳破破爛爛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.00,0:12:31.00,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}這么快就來信物了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.64,0:12:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.07,0:12:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到現在的貝殼中最漂亮的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.48,0:12:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,護身符
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.30,0:12:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.28,0:13:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.64,0:13:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.11,0:13:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.56,0:13:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林檎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.17,0:13:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類也該死 和我們一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.77,0:13:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林檎是機械人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.58,0:14:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機械人小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.18,0:14:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我煩小鬼 小鬼身上有股新的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.52,0:14:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世間正在走向毀滅 不需要小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.70,0:14:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.58,0:14:28.73,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}朱○飛踢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.72,0:14:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開林檎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.04,0:14:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.64,0:14:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.84,0:14:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.61,0:14:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林檎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.47,0:15:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.60,0:15:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.46,0:15:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是卡辛嗎 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.39,0:15:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了你就能停止毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.98,0:15:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不信這麽蠢的傳言
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.04,0:15:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我也知道大家會這麽想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.74,0:15:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會有這麽嶄新的身體 我從來都沒見過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.27,0:16:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是以後再也不會看到了 因為我要捏碎你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.80,0:16:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽 你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.48,0:17:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.27,0:17:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.41,0:17:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.87,0:17:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.95,0:18:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歐吉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.40,0:18:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.77,0:18:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不相信
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.16,0:19:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分別過去悲傷哭泣了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.17,0:19:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.57,0:19:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你的真身
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.12,0:19:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真能搞出這種殺人方法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.83,0:19:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是最差勁的人 從最初開始就
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.85,0:19:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳知道嗎 我的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.56,0:19:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想殺了你的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.81,0:19:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我 我到底是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.78,0:19:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是個殺戮機器
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.96,0:19:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去殺死了名為“月”的太陽 於是毀滅開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.69,0:20:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界已經 死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.75,0:20:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽都不得而知 連自己的事情也
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.00,0:20:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只知道敵人叫我 卡辛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//-------------------ED-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.17,0:20:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 有接受著死亡的機械人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.80,0:20:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 世界充滿了臨終之聲


